<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ A 150-year-old, family-owned cigar company, the last cigar maker in Tampa, Fla., <a href="//www.nytimes.com/2014/07/22/us/after-150-years-of-rolling-them-tampa-is-close-to-no-cigars.html">confronts new tobacco regulations</a>.</p>
