<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ A report concludes that most of <a href="//techcrunch.com/2014/07/21/the-majority-of-todays-app-businesses-are-not-sustainable/?ncid=rss">todayâs app businesses</a> are not sustainable.</p>
